CompressiveNMF          Function for our compressive NMF methods
CompressiveNMF_map      Maximum-a-posteriori for the CompressiveNMF
                        algorithm
plot.CompressiveNMF     Plotting function for CompressiveNMF
plot_DBS_signature      Plot Double-based-substitution signatures
plot_ID_signature       Plot Indel signatures
plot_SBS_signature      Plot SBS signatures
plot_weights            Plot the signature loadings (exposures or
                        weights)
